Package org.bschlangaul.antlr

Interface TexEinbettungListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
TexEinbettungBaseListener
public interface TexEinbettungListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by TexEinbettungParser.
